; Facing program — probes the surface, then makes three roughing passes.
; Demonstrates the G-code outline, cross-file go-to-definition (o<probe> call
; jumps to subs/probe.ngc), block folding, and the formatter.
G21 G90 G54
#<_start_z> = 5

o<probe> call

o<rough> repeat [3]
  G1 X100 F800
  G1 Y10
  G1 X0
o<rough> endrepeat

M2
